lead_paragraph: Robbie Gould took the field as a New York Giant for the first time Sunday as the former Bears kicker made his debut in place of scandal-hit Josh Brown, currently on the NFL commissioner's exempt list.

headline.print_headline: Giants Thin at Safety, Debut New Kicker vs. Rams in London
